<pb facs="1078710" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Doctissimo et toto Orbe Celeberrimo
                <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johanni Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs>.</salute></opener>
<p><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavio</rs> in Adriatici Reginam reversus postquam per
                <lb/>quindecim dierum spatium ibidem commoratus fueram
                <lb/>vocatus ut sanitatem ammissam restituerem Nobi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lissimo <choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>quiti ac <choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Divi</expan></choice> Marci Procuratori Laurentio <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Tie<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>polo</rs> a Patavinis Medicis f<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>re derelicto et pro despe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rato habito; Tuas Vir Clarissime invenio <rs key="B_1714-10-20_991170515019305501" type="letter">litteras</rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti vom 20. Oktober 1714</note>
<lb/>die XX pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teriti Octobris exaratas; atque ex illis
                <lb/>Te semper locutum fuisse de Thaleris uncialibus
                <lb/>Argenti unci<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quipollentibus clar<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> deduco. Ego re<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vera etiam ex pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentibus tuis epistolis semper
                <lb/>collexi, Te pro Thalero imperiali Argenti unciam
                <lb/>intellexisse, tuamque aperui mentem <choice><abbr>Nobiliss:<hi rend="sup">is</hi></abbr><expan>Nobilissimis</expan></choice>
<lb/>Patavini <rs type="organisation">Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>i</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatoribus</rs>: ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m ipsi Amplis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>simi Proceres me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mentis expositioni fidere
                <lb/>ex toto nolentes jusserunt ut non solum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te sci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>scitarer quid pro Thaleri imperialis valore intellige<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>res, ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m etiam ut admonerem Te certo certius
                <lb/>solennibus vocationis litteris per sexennium vocatum
                <lb/>iri cum salario annuo 1500 Thalerorum, 1500 Duca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis Venetis, non autem totidem Argenti unciis <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quipol<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lentium. Ultimam quam ad Te misi <rs key="B_1714-10-05_991170515019405501" type="letter">episto</rs><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1078711" n="2"/>
<lb break="no"/><rs key="B_1714-10-05_991170515019405501" type="letter">lam</rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli vom 05. Oktober 1714</note> ad mentem, et iuxta mandata Trium Amplissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>morum <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatorum</rs> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipu<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> <choice><abbr>v.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice></hi></abbr><expan>v<unclear>er</unclear>o</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Procu.<hi rend="sup">ris</hi></abbr><expan>Procuratoris</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="person">Ruzzini</rs>
<lb/>conscripsi; reliqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> autem <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentes epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Identifizieren!</note> iussu quidem
                <lb/>eorundem Moecenatum quoad aliqua script<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fu<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>re
                <lb/>sed non quoad omnia. Nam in iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> respiciunt Tha<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>leros unciales, ipsi nunquam salarium 1500 Thale<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rorum uncialium proposu<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>re; resque (ut verum
                <lb/>fatear) agebatur inter Te et me, donec tandem
                <lb/>post plures consessus ipsi <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Exce.<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Modera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tores</rs> Tibi <choice><sic>propenere</sic><corr>proponere</corr></choice>, et promittere salarium
                <lb/>annuum 1500 Ducatorum venetorum deliberave<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rint si per sexennium Patavium pro edocendis
                <lb/>disciplinis mathematicis venire non recusaveris.
                <lb/>Vides ergo Vir Celeberrime nunquam Tibi fuisse pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>missum salarium 1500 Thalerorum uncialium
                <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> meis Moecenatibus, qui tuam in omnibus discipli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nis Mathematicis incomparabilem peritiam atque
                <lb/>habilitatem agnoscunt, Teque veluti Mathematico<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum Principem magnifaciunt offerentes salarium
                <lb/>nemini in Patavino <rs type="organisation">Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>o</rs> hactenus persolutum.</p>
<p><rs key="B_1714-10-20_991170515019305501" type="letter">Nuperrimam tuam epistolam</rs><note type="editorial">vom 20. Oktober 1714</note> Amplissimo Mode<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1078712" n="3"/>
<lb break="no"/>ratori <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="person">Ruzzino</rs> ostendere hactenus haud potui; quia
                <lb/>ipse nondum in Patriam redivit. Ruri adhuc perma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>net in aere aprico venationum grati<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>, sed brevi in
                <lb/>Civitatem redibit; atque statim <rs key="B_1714-10-20_991170515019305501" type="letter">nuperri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mam tuam epistolam</rs><note type="editorial">vom 20. Oktober 1714</note> perlegendam ipsi offeram; roga<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bo ut 1500 Thaleros unciales, vel quadringentos Ludo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vicos aureos, Gallis Louis d'or dictos, annuatim Ti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bi offerat atque promittat; statimque Te admo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nebo de omnibus iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in huiusmodi negotio decer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nentur. Interim ut nescias nolo, morem invaluisse
                <lb/>apud Moecenates nostros vocandi solenniter per
                <lb/>sexennium quemcunque Professorem; atqueidcir<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>co, si res tandem successum sortietur, necessum fore
                <lb/>ut facultatem obtineas a <rs type="organisation">Magistratu</rs>, et <rs type="organisation">Senatu</rs>
<lb/>vestro Academico per sexennium ad nos migrandi.</p>
<p>Te rogo <choice><sic>humilimm<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice></sic><corr>humillim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice></corr></choice> Vir Doctissime ut adhuc ex<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pectes unicam meam super hac re epistolam, quam ad
                <lb/>Te mittam statim ac potuerim alloqui Amplissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                <lb/><choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Divi</expan></choice> Marci <choice><abbr>Proc.<hi rend="sup">rem</hi></abbr><expan>Procuratorem</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="person">Ruzzinum</rs> qui propediem adveniet.</p> <closer><salute>Vale, et ad omnia mandata tua me paratissimum crede.</salute>
<lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1714-11-09">9 <choice><abbr>Nov.<hi rend="sup">bris</hi></abbr><expan>Novembris</expan></choice> 1714</date>.</dateline></closer>
<postscript><p>P. S. Ducatus venetus sesquifloreno Germanico <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quipollet.
          <lb/>Salutem plurimam dico <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimo</expan></choice> Agnato tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao</rs>.</p></postscript>
